TASK #1
-------
*Primorial Numbers*

Submitted by: Mohammad S Anwar

Write a script to generate first 10 Primorial Numbers.


    Primorial numbers are those formed by multiplying successive prime numbers.


For example,

 P(0) = 1    (1)
 P(1) = 2    (1x2)
 P(2) = 6    (1x2×3)
 P(3) = 30   (1x2×3×5)
 P(4) = 210  (1x2×3×5×7)

=end comment
